items.title: Altherr's slam off Kershaw wins it for Phillies
items.summary: Aaron Altherr launched the first grand slam Clayton Kershaw has allowed with two outs in the sixth inning Monday night as the Phillies stunned the Dodgers with a 4-3 comeback win at Citizens Bank Park that delayed the visitors' National League West clinch party at least another day.
